high_descs: enter a room with a desk
pick up pot from the desk
walk with pot to the fridge
place pot inside fridge, pick up pot from the fridge
walk with pot to the countertop
Turn right and then left and go to the dining table in the room.
Pick up the copper pot on the table.
Leave the room take a right and go to the fridge on your left.
Put the pot in the fridge and then take it back out.
Turn left and go to the counter next to the microwave.
Place pot on the counter in front of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled pot next to the microwave on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the desk.
Take the pot from the desk.
Turn around and go near the fridge.
Put the pot into the fridge.
Then take it out and go near the counter top.
Put the pot on the counter top.
anns.task_desc: Placed the pot on the counter top.
